{
  "stem": "24163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had the most gruesome experience of my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like, rather than tell you about it, read a letter which I wrote to my wife, which is rather explicit and tells you about my experience.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The letter is dated-- this is the original letter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I keep it because I think it has sort of historic meaning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It does to me, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the original letter, as you can see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it is dated May the 3rd, 1945 with a news clipping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The news clipping describes the capture of the Dachau concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I believe I cut this out of the-- there was an American Army newspaper called And I only included this clipping.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is the letter. 'My dearest honey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What I saw yesterday is really too horrible to write about, but I will make an attempt to recall all of the horrors I saw and hope that you can take it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this is not a sugar report.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had an opportunity to visit the notorious concentration camp at Dachau along with our chaplain.' They had called that they needed chaplains and doctors, I believe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were close by, so our chaplain then requisition a Jeep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went with him as his interpreter, again, to the camp. 'You can see by enclosed report that we liberated the camp and its inmates just a few days ago.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I am glad that I was able to see all of its horrors right after we killed the last SS man in charge.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And here is what I saw.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
